OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jim Grant
OL,5,FJim Grant, Age 98, Royal Marines
OL,7,FInterviewed 30 July 2023
OL,9,FA Royal Marine who manned a gun on a
OL,10,FLanding Craft Flak on D-Day, Mr
OL,11,FGrant's crew spent many hours off
OL,12,Fshore laying covering fire for
OL,13,Fsoldiers running up the beaches.
OL,15,FThey also landed some troops
OL,16,Fthemselves. LCFs were equipped with
OL,17,Fanti-aircraft guns to provide air
OL,18,Fcover for the troop-carrying landing
OL,19,Fcraft.
