OL,5,FThose vessels looked very similar but
OL,6,Fdid not have adequate firepower to
OL,7,Fdefend themselves against air attack.
OL,9,FLCFs were remodelled versions of the
OL,10,Flanding craft designed to carry tanks
OL,11,Fand heavy vehicles.
OL,13,FMr Grant said: "I was on LCF 29.
OL,15,F"We had been going up and down the
OL,16,FChannel up until D-Day and then they
OL,17,Fsent us in. When D-Day came they just
OL,18,Fsent us straight over.
