OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jim Grant
OL,5,F"We had four Pom Poms one in each
OL,6,Fcorner of the craft and we had eight
OL,7,FOerlikons (both of these were anti-
OL,8,Faircraft guns) on board. We lived on
OL,9,Fboard and slept in hammocks.
OL,11,F"We had a message to pick up the
OL,12,FCanadians at the Isle of Wight and
OL,13,Ftake them over.
OL,15,F"They put them in small boats. They
OL,16,Fwere all sick when they got there.
