OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jim Grant
OL,5,F"All they were doing was lying on the
OL,6,Fbeach being sick. I don't think we
OL,7,Fwere really prepared for what
OL,8,Fhappened. We was firing over the tops
OL,9,Fof their heads.
OL,11,F"Anybody on board who didn't have a
OL,12,Fparticular job on the gun they sent
OL,13,Fthem in with and they joined in with
OL,14,Fthe troops that was invading.
OL,16,F"I was on a Pom-Pom and my job was to
OL,17,Fshoot at anything that we didn't want
OL,18,Fthere.
