OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jim Grant
OL,5,F"We were firing over the tops of their
OL,6,Fheads hoping to hit the target on the
OL,7,Fother side. Our main job was firing at
OL,8,Fthe aircraft but anything really.
OL,10,F"One came down and we thought it was
OL,11,Fgoing to hit us.
OL,13,F"It turned off to starboard and went
OL,14,Finto the sea.
OL,16,F"There was an explosion and it blew us
OL,17,Fsideways. It must have gone off when
OL,18,Fit hit the bottom of the sea."
